summary: Since graduating from the HAS University of Applied Sciences in the Netherlands with a degree in Horticulture & Business Management, I have enthusiastically begun my professional career as an assistant tomato grower at Windset Farms in Delta, BC to further my interest, knowledge, and experience in greenhouse fruit & vegetable production.
